title: 'Pragmastat: Pragmatic Statistical Toolkit'
abstract: 'This manual presents a toolkit of statistical procedures that provide
  reliable results across diverse real-world distributions, with ready-to-use
  implementations and detailed explanations. The toolkit consists of renamed,
  recombined, and refined versions of existing methods.
  Written for software developers, mathematicians, and LLMs.'
